[
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "1",
    "Text": "He frowned and turned &#761;his attention&#762; away,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "2",
    "Text": "&#761;simply&#762; because the blind man came to him &#761;interrupting&#762;.<span class='fn' foot_note=30052>1</span>"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "3",
    "Text": "You never know &#761;O Prophet&#762;, perhaps he may be purified,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "4",
    "Text": "or he may be mindful, benefitting from the reminder."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "5",
    "Text": "As for the one who was indifferent,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "6",
    "Text": "you gave him your &#761;undivided&#762; attention,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "7",
    "Text": "even though you are not to blame if he would not be purified."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "8",
    "Text": "But as for the one who came to you, eager &#761;to learn&#762;,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "9",
    "Text": "being in awe &#761;of Allah&#762;,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "10",
    "Text": "you were inattentive to him."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "11",
    "Text": "But no! This &#761;revelation&#762; is truly a reminder."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "12",
    "Text": "So let whoever wills be mindful of it."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "13",
    "Text": "It is &#761;written&#762; on pages held in honour&mdash;"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "14",
    "Text": "highly esteemed, purified&mdash;"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "15",
    "Text": "by the hands of angel-scribes,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "16",
    "Text": "honourable and virtuous."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "17",
    "Text": "Condemned are &#761;disbelieving&#762; humans! How ungrateful they are &#761;to Allah&#762;!"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "18",
    "Text": "From what substance did He create them?"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "19",
    "Text": "He created them from a sperm-drop, and ordained their development."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "20",
    "Text": "Then He makes the way easy for them,<span class='fn' foot_note=30053>1</span>"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "21",
    "Text": "then causes them to die and be buried.<span class='fn' foot_note=30054>1</span>"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "22",
    "Text": "Then when He wills, He will resurrect them."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "23",
    "Text": "But no! They have failed to comply with what He ordered."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "24",
    "Text": "Let people then consider their food:"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "25",
    "Text": "how We pour down rain in abundance"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "26",
    "Text": "and meticulously split the earth open &#761;for sprouts&#762;,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "27",
    "Text": "causing grain to grow in it,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "28",
    "Text": "as well as grapes and greens,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "29",
    "Text": "and olives and palm trees,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "30",
    "Text": "and dense orchards,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "31",
    "Text": "and fruit and fodder&mdash;"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "32",
    "Text": "all as &#761;a means of&#762; sustenance for you and your animals."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "33",
    "Text": "Then, when the Deafening Blast<span class='fn' foot_note=30055>1</span>&nbsp;comes to pass&mdash;"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "34",
    "Text": "on that Day every person will flee from their own siblings,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "35",
    "Text": "and &#761;even&#762; their mother and father,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "36",
    "Text": "and &#761;even&#762; their spouse and children."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "37",
    "Text": "For then everyone will have enough concern of their own."
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "38",
    "Text": "On that Day &#761;some&#762; faces will be bright,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "39",
    "Text": "laughing and rejoicing,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "40",
    "Text": "while &#761;other&#762; faces will be dusty,"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "41",
    "Text": "cast in gloom&mdash;"
  },
  {
    "BookCode": "MKT",
    "SurahNumber": "80",
    "AyahNumber": "42",
    "Text": "those are the disbelievers, the &#761;wicked&#762; sinners."
  }
]
